org.semanticweb.rulewerk.core.model.implementation

Class TermFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.semanticweb.rulewerk.core.model.implementation.TermFactory

  • public class TermFactory
extends Object
    Class for creating various kinds of terms. Instances of this class maintain an internal cache that allows them to re-use the generated objects, which is useful to safe memory since the same term is often needed in multiple places.
    Author:
    Markus Kroetzsch
